":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99411be2da8480e1a069245eb36a9463a66610da","tid":2202000,"uid":283557,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔見你肯交出同佳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"交返曾矮仔老豆條屍俾你就得，都係逃犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401e60f8ffe6bb7378b6e0be9df05aeef585bf15","tid":2202000,"uid":139117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"又唔見大陸送返個12個人返嚟？"},{"pid":"efc48a1abc332f06972d63de0ef10f259dea2ca7","tid":2202000,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">傳5名偷渡港人遭扣 陸委會：不針對個案說明</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/09/12 22:41<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者賴言曦台北12日電）媒體工作者鐘聖雄今天在臉書發文說，5名經東沙島偷渡來台的香港「反送中」抗爭者已被扣留近2個月。<span class=\"red\">陸委會則回應，希望外界勿作不必要揣測，政府也不會針對個案加以說明。</span><br />\n<br />\n大陸委員會今天晚間以書面形式應詢回應，對於外界流傳的各項訊息，陸委會認為或有其特定目的，對整個機制或個人可能造成傷害。<span class=\"red\">政府對港人已設人道援助機制，符合條件者都會給予必要的人道援助。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009120183.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202009120183.aspx&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=ff9b9803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009120183.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"2323206568a1068d816a45332862269c94c0e0e0","tid":2202000,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d98f6724cef15e69f9e5ad8f99372381ce1dc6a1","tid":2202000,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99411be2da8480e1a069245e