ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81542bf55cf3d170fce54a6e03b482acebf17dc","tid":2202000,"uid":51057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"5名港人去左台灣<br />\n港共: 希望台方將5人送回香港，讓港府依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n12名港人被支那捉走<br />\n港共: 特區政府不希望外地司法管轄區干涉特區的執法，因此尊重不會干預其他司法管轄區的執法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}